<paragraph id="8BB1D67CFFD21E1383BDFA7502478DDE" blockId="32.[151,684,1413,1666]" pageId="32" pageNumber="91">
<emphasis id="B97A0A6EFFD21E1383BDFA7502C58D12" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="91">
Plantae 10-15(-20) cm altae, cormo depresso-campanulato 
